      "comment": "PAW ELODEE (5) has a strong winning strike-rate here having won two of three starts. Hit the frame latest (23.96) when second at Traralgon in a Grade 5. Rates on top and should go close. PAW DANGER (7) has missed the frame at his last couple but wasn't beaten far three back when third (24.58) at Sale in a Grade 5. Well placed here and can atone this time. PAW FABLE (3) settled midfield in the run and boxed on to finish there when 4th (30.17) at Sandown. Has performed well from this box with a win and four minor placings to his name from nine starts. Worth another chance. PAW CALLIE (1) can fill a top-three spot.",
